Here are all the commands to run the project:

1. Start Ollama (required for AI)
ollama serve

In a separate terminal, pull the models if not already done:
ollama pull llama3
ollama pull nomic-embed-text

2. Start Backend (Flask API)
cd /Users/sumanshuarora/Documents/coding/only_flask_new/InternalKnowledgeHub/backend
source .venv/bin/activate
flask run --host=0.0.0.0 --port=5000

3. Start Frontend (React)
cd /Users/sumanshuarora/Documents/coding/only_flask_new/InternalKnowledgeHub/frontend
npm run dev
